{"tid":1065881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［安樂死］日本5ch有個post討論安樂死","createTime":"2019-03-17T14:39:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T18:40:55.000Z","uid":160807,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f73b03a23e448d0aa9114f14f22812f322952986","tid":1065881,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"香港根本須要安樂死合法化<br />\n但係政府一直冇重視安樂死訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通想安樂死就一定拎昂貴費用去其他國家？<br />\n<br />\n5ch相信大家都聽過，係一個同連登好相似既討論區<br />\n我地亦都可以稱呼佢為日本連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本人對高質死亡既追求就無香港咁保守<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個度一直都有啲post比大家純粹傾下自己心目中理想既死法<br />\n比較下各式各樣既死法同摸索下啲新既死法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以亦都有啲自行安樂死既研究方法<br />\n<br />\n作者一開始帶左已經頭盔都話係純學術研究<br />\n唔係推薦自殺呢種做法<br />\n有興趣可以睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【首吊り･練炭】自殺方法研究スレ16【飛び降り･ヘリウム等】<br />\n<a href=\"http://krsw.5ch.net/test/read.cgi/mental/1543474374/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkrsw.5ch.net%2Ftest%2Fread.cgi%2Fmental%2F1543474374%2F&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F4R92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=0230db33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://krsw.5ch.net/test/read.cgi/mental/1543474374/</a><br />\n<br />\n真心覺得日本仔係對世界貢獻緊安樂死既進步<br />\n利申：純學術研究"},{"pid":"24310911350f28a4d847603cb1da268d13a69882","tid":1065881,"uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:45:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgi1V4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffgi1V4P.png&h=e152f20d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0826e7332be7e6e83e56dcacefd5cc934787056","tid":1065881,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fgi1V4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffgi1V4P.png&h=e152f20d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"709ba30d03788304241762197defbc7b3a58af11","tid":1065881,"uid":209487,"like":2,"dislike":66,"score":-64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f4cd2108da002326a9e9d5918c6aab0f6810cef","tid":1065881,"uid":61882,"like":10,"dislike":17,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:01:06.000Z","msg":"本主題可能正在討論有關「自殺」的內容。<br />\n若你需要進一步協助，可致電以下求助熱線：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/help/suicide-crisis-helpline</a>"},{"pid":"066f51a99381e1825d92d7a3d2bfb635211b677f","tid":1065881,"uid":160807,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"709ba30d03788304241762197defbc7b3a58af11","tid":1065881,"uid":209487,"like":2,"dislike":66,"score":-64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:01:11.000Z","msg":"選擇死亡一直係避忌話題<br />\n人有自由死既權利<br />\n因為人始終要面對死亡<br />\n唔理你係中國人定日本人<br />\n就算外星人都會死"},{"pid":"e6b0932b524480e7e32f73f076bdab5596180ea1","tid":1065881,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":12,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:03:15.000Z","msg":"我支持安樂死<br />\n但只限植物人或要依賴維生儀器生存嘅人<br />\n同埋老人痴呆症同老人"},{"pid":"d3497487bd4aad9a6d08fc48a0fbc1077443039d","tid":1065881,"uid":5739,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"香港連「生」都搞唔好，仲要搞「死」？"},{"pid":"9b76580996a926d3c88298200a40bc76fedbe931","tid":1065881,"uid":160807,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T15:19:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/fgi1V4P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ffgi1V4P.png&h=45465954&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e223591e918e0f9b1eb3e656b633b12a206b89e","tid":1065881,"uid":160807,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e6b0932b524480e7e32f73f